            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1625647034838-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>conchiglie</strong> to a pot of <strong>boiled water</strong> with a large pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Cook the <strong>conchiglie</strong> for 10-12 min or until cooked with a slight bite</p><p>Once done, drain the <strong>conchiglie </strong>and return it to the pot</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
