    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the<strong> basil </strong>roughly, including the stalks, then add it to a <strong>food processor</strong> with the<strong> flaked almonds</strong>, 2/3 of the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> (save some for garnish!), 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span><strong> olive oil</strong>, 2 tbsp<span class=\"text-danger\"> [4 tbsp] </span><strong>cold water</strong> and the juice of 1/2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[1]<strong> </span>lemon</strong></p><p>Season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>basil pesto</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
